{"tid":2373260,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"兒子讀書壓力大　港媽移居吉隆坡：在香港參與學校面試，感覺是求老師收我兒子！","createTime":"2021-01-20T10:08:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-21T19:38:24.000Z","uid":209657,"like":21,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"6e0cd7ef495a74f2cdb1cf41cc0506f21b60624e","tid":2373260,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T10:08:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2845000/2845852/4_1024.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2845000%2F2845852%2F4_1024.jpeg&h=3c3bac0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n育有一名7歲兒子的港媽Mari，有感香港教育制度「太壓迫」，決定舉家移民馬來西亞吉隆坡，為兒子提供更理想的成長環境。Mari兒子現時就讀九龍塘一所私校，每月學費近港幣一萬元，回想以往跟兒子準備學校面試，她坦言好驚、很大壓力。她指在香港讀書甚為辛苦，不只逼迫小朋友，家長也要參與其中，陪同小朋友讀書、做功課、參與面試班。<br />\n<br />\n轉換環境生活的念頭逐漸成形，Mari也沒想到，一次旅行竟成了移民的契機。在2020年年頭，Mari一家到馬來西亞探望朋友，住了兩星期。在旅途當中，她對當地的觀感甚佳，「居住舒適、物價不高、沒那麼大壓力」。朋友知道她對國際學校Taylor's International School有興趣，便帶她到學校參觀。"},{"pid":"8ee851644f74d8f7dee7504b15eea9ecf16b76d7","tid":2373260,"uid":91833,"like":3,"dislike":16,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T10:10:16.000Z","msg":"？？ 小孩不笨一話如果E依班<br />\n係永不超生嘅垃圾"},{"pid":"f42754dab851773fee6934301d7e94ce88786c38","tid":2373260,"uid":91833,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"8ee851644f74d8f7dee7504b15eea9ecf16b76d7","tid":2373260,"uid":91833,"like":3,"dislike":16,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T10:10:16.000Z","msg":"？？ 小孩不笨一話如果E依班<br />\n係永不超生嘅垃圾"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T10:10:50.000Z","msg":"自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以為新加坡"},{"pid":"00f93df20073c0e7f9cf5c58abff9f186f026df8","tid":2373260,"uid":209657,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T10:11:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2845000/2845852/15_1024.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2845000%2F2845852%2F15_1024.jpeg&h=a1eb22f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n踏進校園，Mari立即被偌大校舍吸引，兒子參觀過後也表示非常喜歡大草地、操場、游泳地、圖書館等設施。<br />\n<br />\nMari指學校老師態度和善，以往在香港參與學校面試，感覺是求老師收我的兒子；現在則『反客為主』，我可以為兒子選擇學校，他們亦歡迎兒子入讀。<br />\n<br />\n至於教學及課程方面，Mari留意到該校任教英文的老師都是外籍老師，認為在語言教學上有優勢，可以令兒子學好英文。她亦有感學校課程多元化，設Minecraft課程，將小朋友愛玩的遊戲融入教學當中。<br />\n<br />\nMari指出，該校學生在回家之前已完成所有功課，減輕家長的壓力，小朋友也有多些時間玩樂及休息。"},{"pid":"6341e22872d8579651f9977d13c2e1006d94f3a1","tid":2373260,"uid":18477,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T10:12:33.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">今次輪到石鏡泉報呀？<br />\n<br />\n仲乜咁快又開個移民馬來亞po呀？</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77a5b01f77655a4f4e2fa1398a23ae5c16e829b1","tid":2373260,"uid":18477,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"6341e22872d8579651f9977d13c2e1006d94f3a1","tid":2373260,"uid":18477,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T10:12:33.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">今次輪到石鏡泉報呀？<br />\n<br />\n仲乜咁快又開個移民馬來亞po呀？</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T10:13:10.000Z","msg":"港媽14萬全家移居馬來西亞 3千港元租2,000呎屋：成家都變得開朗！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2367713\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2367713</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">同一個user開</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"8a2c864edc1cef8062581be233d9134dad3e82d2","tid":2373260,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T10:13:41.000Z","msg":"但係馬來西亞航空好危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fce25483f48916ec9a8bb925a1061a8faa3686a5","tid":2373260,"uid":209657,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T10:16:25.000Z","msg":"參觀過後，Mari對校園環境及課程甚為滿意，決定即場和兒子進行面試，並獲取錄成為插班生。<br />\n<br />\n不過受疫情影響，至今未能成行。Mari指一收到取錄通知，便替兒子交學費。現時兒子就讀九龍塘一所私校，每月學費近港幣一萬元；馬來西亞的國際學校學費較為便宜，需約8,000多港元。<br />\n<img src=\"https://schooladvisor.my/admin/uploads/images/school/186/gallery/1-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fschooladvisor.my%2Fadmin%2Fuploads%2Fimages%2Fschool%2F186%2Fgallery%2F1-1.jpg&h=7413ddb5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2264fdf7a35f5f7b1a5f5d748dcabb818d51738b","tid":2373260,"uid":137159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a2c864edc1cef8062581be233d9134dad3e82d2","tid":2373260,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T10:13:41.000Z","msg":"但係馬來西亞航空好危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T10:17:59.000Z","msg":"唔怕，馬拉政府話唔再注資馬航，好快會執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"159dee9560f762a1398a086023d372a7644a2961","tid":2373260,"uid":209657,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T10:20:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2845000/2845852/9_1024.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2845000%2F2845852%2F9_1024.jpeg&h=8bc1dc50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMari早在兩年前以港幣約400萬購入吉隆坡市中心8 Conlay的樓花，她坦言那時只用作投資，沒打算自住；決定移民之後，700呎單位正好成了一家人的「安樂窩」。Mari指選擇8 Conlay的原因，在於大樓景觀優美、交通方便，就近地標雙子塔；單位裝修美觀，附送傢俬，一收樓即可入住。<br />\n<br />\n對於移居馬來西亞的生活，Mari甚是期待，指自己不會覺得過了異鄉生活，因有許多朋友在當地居住；她希望疫情趕快過去，一家大小可以轉換環境，享受悠閒寫意的生活。"},{"pid":"b8dac0e3e9fd1fde9b56b0db4752684ccc39194d","tid":2373260,"uid":8308,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T10:21:50.000Z","msg":"馬拉要諗清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能要二次移民"},{"pid":"8e5fe48c6a4c987d003e488a22773f545d2fa4bd","tid":2373260,"uid":209657,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T10:23:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2845000/2845852/10_1024.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2845000%2F2845852%2F10_1024.jpeg&h=25484c9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2845000/2845852/8_1024.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2845000%2F2845852%2F8_1024.jpeg&h=16ce3d26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2845000/2845852/14_1024.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2845000%2F2845852%2F14_1024.jpeg&h=3ce4c384&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"985516aed34e854b24eed81b3faff1f7b4eb19d9","tid":2373260,"uid":5220,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"6341e22872d8579651f9977d13c2e1006d94f3a1","tid":2373260,"uid":18477,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T10:12:33.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">今次輪到石鏡泉報呀？<br />\n<br />\n仲乜咁快又開個移民馬來亞po呀？</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T10:23:31.000Z","msg":"騙局緊係要不停宣傳引人入局啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi